<A>__{landon tears down the steps. past his mother to the front door. he's out the door before she even turns around.}
<L>__{interior parsonage reverend sullivan's bedroom midnight}
<A>__{reverend sullivan sits up in bed. his feet find slippers on the floor. he looks haggard, his hair thinner, his face defeated.}
